body.name: Jocisland LED Bed Frame Queen Size with Charging Station Upholstered Bed Frame with Headboard Storage Motion Activated Night Light, No Box Spring Needed, Light Grey
features: Queen Bed Frame Tall Headboard: Extra tall 53.2" button tufted,nailhead trim wingback headboard with velvet upholstery makes your bed the centerpiece of bedroom, providing much more comfortable support.
LED Bed Frame with Motion Nightlight: The RGB LED light supports 20 color variations. The warm nightlight under the queen size bed frame turns on when you are near the bed for a convenient nighttime.

Storage Headboard with Charging Station: The queen LED bed frame with storage headboard keeps small essentials like phones, glasses, and books within easy reach. 2 USB ports keep your electronics at 100% power.
Stable & Noiseless: Sturdy integrated bed frame construction with bolt-on rails design to provide solid support. EVA Strip is attached to firmly hold the mattress in place and prevent noise.
Easy to Assemble: All the components of this queen bed frame with LED lights clearly labeled and numbered, and you just need to match the numbers to assemble. Two people recommended.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE THIS BED!
reviews.reviewText: It took me 2 hours to put together by myself and the directions were very clear. All the lights are dope and the ones under the bed are motion sense and sensitive. Material is super soft as well. OnlyComplaint is the stickers with the numbers are impossible to get off in one swoop. Bed is sturdy asf. All the hardware was good! Only have had it one night so not sure on longevity or how it sustains motion lol but upon completion of assembly it’s cool! Doesn’t look cheap at all. And the lights have a bunch of options. If you want this bed definitely get it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Such a great bedframe!!!! 5 ⭐️
reviews.reviewText: This purchase was for sure worth it. The bedframe is very sturdy and stable. There is zero noise when getting on the bed, being in it, moving around, it’s very quiet which I love so much. It sits very low to the ground so be aware of that. I think it’s a beautiful bed frame and looks great in person. The led lights and motion sensor lights are both neat and work as they should. It’s a very heavy bed frame to move around in the box, 2 people is preferred to move it. I did all the putting together of the bed frame and moving it around myself, but having 2 people would help a lot. It does take time to put together the frame, every bit of 2+ hours, but it’s worth it I promise. The fabric feels nice to the touch, I love the recessed area above the headboard, it’s nice for holding my phone and the built in charging ports are amazing to have and convenient. I definitely recommend this bed frame to anyone who is looking at this product. I was skeptical about buying it at first because at the time there were no reviews and it was newly released on Amazon, but I went for it and I’m happy I did. My package had no damage to it whatsoever, all parts and pieces were included, nothing was missing. I highly recommend this bed frame to anyone interested in a new queen size frame like I was.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Absolutely love this bed frame, it is short than expected but when you think about how tall normal bed frames are it’s definitely taller. The LED lights are SIIICCKKKK. The motion sensory lights are also a nice touch, works as a great nightlight for when you need to use the bathroom in the middle of the night. The material it’s made from is soft and good quality. It took awhile to put together but definitely worth it it’s sturdy and doesn’t move around or make noises doesn’t feel cheap. Sometimes with bed frames your pillows sink down into the crack behind your pillow but with this bed frame it keeps the bed in place against the bed frame so your pillows don’t do that. Would definitely be careful about stubbing your toe when making the bed though but I mean as with any bed frame it’s tradition. WORTH EVERY PENNY.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Item as described.
reviews.reviewText: The bed looks nice and looks like the picture on the site, only thing I see as a negative is the headboard isn't as tall as I expected but nothing to give it less stars for. The lights work well and the whole setup was pretty straightforward with the picture diagrams. Seems very sturdy, and it came boxed well and nothing was damaged. I will say that because of the weight of the item don't expect the carrier to put it in the appropriate place when they deliver it because of the weight. It will definitely take two people at least to get into the house and in your room. Feels really nice to the touch. Don't regret the purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this bed frame!
reviews.reviewText: The bed frame beat my expectations! It's very sturdy and the instructions are fairly clear. The only problem I had were issues with the holes for wire control as they were just slightly to large for the screws.
